WhatNew Buyer Protection Policy

WhatNew Support May 16, 2025 at 7:02 PM.

How Shipping Works on WhatNew

USPS Ground Advantage (Packages under 1 lb)

WhatNew charges commercial USPS Ground Advantage Package Service rates for lighter packages (less than 1 lb).

USPS First-Class Mail Letter Service (Special Cases)

For packages that meet the following eligibility requirements, WhatNew offers USPS First-Class Mail Letter Service Rates:

  • Weighs less than 3 ounces
  • Total value is less than ₹20
  • All enclosed items are cards from Sports Cards, TCG categories, and Stickers only
  • No more than 5 cards in the shipment
  • Order is shipped from a US address to another US address

Learn more about USPS First-Class Mail Letter shipping here.

Packages 1 – 5 lbs (Priority Mail)

For all packages weighing 1 – 5 lbs or where the seller has Flat Rate packaging selected (up to 70 lbs), WhatNew charges ₹9.21 (₹8.77 + fees)* for most deliveries in the United States and ships via Priority Mail.

Hawaii, Alaska, U.S. Territories and military bases are excluded.

Packages 5 – 70 lbs

These will ship via USPS Priority Mail by default, and USPS Ground Advantage if opted in. Pricing is based on weight, distance, and dimensions, starting at ₹8.91.

Items over 1 cubic foot in volume will be charged based on dimensional weight.

Example: How Shipping Is Calculated in a Livestream

Let’s take a buyer based in Los Angeles, CA who just purchased a pack of sports cards from a seller in Boston, MA.

  • This qualifies as a Zone 8 shipment as it is cross-country.
  • A pack of sports cards weighing 4 oz costs ₹4.13 to ship (commercial USPS Ground Advantage rates).
  • A second 4 oz pack adds only ₹0.31 (8 oz costs ₹4.44).
  • Adding sneakers weighing 2 lbs adds ₹3.91, reaching ₹9.21 total.
  • Once a buyer is charged ₹9.21, they can add items up to 5 lbs for ₹0 additional shipping cost.

Bundling Logic

WhatNew automatically bundles marketplace and livestream orders to save shipping costs until the seller prints the shipping label. Marketplace and livestream orders are bundled separately.

Additional Livestream Shipping Details

  • Sellers can offer Free or Reduced Shipping to buyers, covering some or all shipping costs.
  • For shipments over 5 lbs, sellers can use Flat-Rate Packaging (₹9.21) or Ground Advantage (from ₹8.91).
  • The Smart Bundling™ tool bundles and unbundles orders to keep shipping costs low. Some orders may ship in multiple packages.
